{"tid":699680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭定康評梁天琦案　中國外交部：堅決反對外部勢力干預香港","createTime":"2018-06-12T17:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T02:00:18.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"44d9fc029fa1e070417e8efe9963d866a6ea071f","tid":699680,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T17:22:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/1707094689376144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F1707094689376144&d=EEZk%2BT5EZvFaVqujkLbSxNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5de9dcb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/1707094689376144</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/lord-01_hoi5k_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flord-01_hoi5k_1200x0.png&h=9ddc4b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本土民主前線前發言人梁天琦因涉及旺角騷亂，被判暴動罪罪成被判囚 6 年。前港督彭定康指，暴動罪所涉及的《公安條例》中有字眼定義模糊令條例易被濫用，被用作政治用途對泛民主派和社運人士作極端判決。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人耿爽回應有關問題時指出，香港是中國特區，香港的事務完全是中國內政，堅決反對任何外部勢力干預香港事務和特區的司法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung 外部勢力咪就係中國囉。<br />\n<br />\nFranking Bull 地上最愛干擾別人的正是中國<br />\n<br />\nNj Wai 一個國家外交部發言人同街市婆無分別！<br />\n<br />\nAit Lee 肥彭係內部勢力喎<br />\n<br />\nPeter S. Wong 咁中共又干預南北韓！<br />\n<br />\nJackie Cho 香港嘅事關佢忍事？<br />\n<br />\nPiu Mok 作句新穎啦！"},{"pid":"46aec0edec2f33d6b1574d64fd572576bd5a6a1a","tid":699680,"uid":114754,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T17:23:56.000Z","msg":"真係唔洗估都知口交部會點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92dca419862c38041c78e6e0dac514a8f46b7dc","tid":699680,"uid":13115,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T17:25:00.000Z","msg":"口交部又衝出黎柒<br />\n蚛蟈或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hk